{"tid":1447870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停撚咩！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:09.000Z","uid":300478,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d969f4ef3d5b9d5555b3e20ced58a27fb67cd66","tid":1447870,"uid":300478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:38.000Z","msg":"之前有人出過好多post話文宣唔到位<br />\n<strong>咁係唔係唔文宣啊？？？？？</strong><br />\n喂大佬前線手足戰略有問題咁係唔係應該<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>改善戰略啊！！！！！！</strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n做咩突然話前線手足全面退場？退到幾時？退倒2014？？？？？<br />\n要唔要出場係前線決定<br />\n如果大家真係咁想要民意就唔該大大力搞文宣！<br />\n向市民同全世界解釋我地做緊咩同點解要咁做！<br />\n<br />\n前線手足要考慮嘅係<br />\n1. 夠唔夠人<br />\n2. 仲有冇力<br />\n3. 有冇一致目標（eg set完rb就走？留守？升級？）<br />\n4. 可唔可以安全離開（研究地形，交通，附近民居）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位大佬幫手諗吓戰略好過啦我求下大家啦</span>"},{"pid":"1f45f1e2070ebe84a41b84a6fbcc4faa3351099e","tid":1447870,"uid":300478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:18.000Z","msg":"我都唔知應該開咩台是但啦唉"},{"pid":"e31d676a2b3d6cbf916dfe24539cf73d3a7e0dfd","tid":1447870,"uid":14680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"利申勇武<br />\n但覺得喺未有好既戰略同對策前唔可以再出去送頭"},{"pid":"8db3b4e6c2284ef02d46fc98bef4a730e64afee8","tid":1447870,"uid":293624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"但而家有狗做臥底滲透之下好容易又出事，建議真係要停一停諗下對策先。"},{"pid":"5813828dd1a33e717f652700788fd6dab5ba2739","tid":1447870,"uid":201095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n「警察還眼」聽日812 1點機場要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"24ba6e2d4642db70a3539bfc3fbe68717661934e","tid":1447870,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"co